title: Why You Wouldn T Survive World War 3

sources.title: Why You Wouldn T Survive World War 3
sources.description: Today we're going to show you exactly why you won't survive World War 3 and the nuclear fallout! You may think you have survival skills, but World War 3 will be unlike any other war previous. It will be a nuclear war that will encompass the entire globe, and if you do somehow manage to survive the initial bombing, you definitely won't survive what comes next! Check out our new video to find out why World War 3 will be the end of all humanity.
